<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="2a8wwg" data-video-descrip="Founded by Com Truise, Religitology worships Herman, the creator of the universe. They apparently regularly practice brainwashing and needless mass-killing for conversion, brainwashing Anthony and turning him into a Manchurian agent." data-video-title="Religitology" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/2a8wwg_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/2a8wwg.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/ChurchOfHappyology" data-video-tropename="Church of Happyology" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="4.83" data-video-rating-count="6" data-video-media-sources="WebVideo/Smosh" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link featured-widget-vid">
