<h1 id="overlay-title">Religitology</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Founded by Com Truise, Religitology worships Herman, the creator of the universe. They apparently regularly practice brainwashing and needless mass-killing for conversion, brainwashing Anthony and turning him into a Manchurian agent.	</p>
